GOAL IS TO MATCH THE MEMBERS USING FIRST NAME LAST NAME AND PHONE NUMBER COMBINATION FOR THE CURRENT REPORT MONTH , IN JANUARY WITH ACTIVE FLAG = 1

YOU CAN JOIN DIM MEMBER AND MEMBER REPORT MONTH BECAUSE DIM MEMBER DOESNT HAVE PHONE NUMBER 

USING A QUERY LIKE THIS 

PLEASE MODIFY THE BEFLOW QUERY TO GET THE ABOVE DETAILS 



WITH input_names (MEMBER_FIRST_NAME, MEMBER_LAST_NAME, MEMBER) AS (
    SELECT * FROM VALUES
        ('AAA', 'BBB'),
        ('CCC BYRONMATLOCK', 'VVV'),
        ('CCC', 'GGGG'),
         ('DDD LAWANDAWIGGS', 'GG'),
TTT        ('WENDELL', 'ULDRICH'),
        ('XX', 'BB'),
        ('HH', 'QQ'),
         ('NNN', 'AA'),
          ('KK', 'LL JOY')
        
        -- add all 86 records here
)
SELECT
    i.MEMBER_FIRST_NAME,
    i.MEMBER_LAST_NAME,
    CASE 
        WHEN t.MEMBER_FIRST_NAME IS NOT NULL THEN 'FOUND'
        ELSE 'NOT FOUND'
    END AS status
FROM input_names i
LEFT JOIN FWRB_PRD_WMIDR_DB.BI_ANALYSIS.DIM_MEMBER t
    ON UPPER(i.MEMBER_FIRST_NAME) = UPPER(t.MEMBER_FIRST_NAME)
   AND UPPER(i.MEMBER_LAST_NAME)  = UPPER(t.MEMBER_LAST_NAME);




